<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Wilderness | Create a new post</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.5.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bulma@0.9.4/css/bulma.min.css">
    <script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/variables.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/create-post.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Press+Start+2P&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    
    <% if(community == 'terrestrial') { %>
        <h1 class="text-center header"><span>🌄</span> Plains and Mountains <span>🌄</span></h1>
        <p class="text-center description">There is a huge variety of wonderful species that you can 
            find in this habitat.<br> From <span>🐵</span> to <span>🐴</span> to <span>🦁</span> to <span>🦌</span> to <span>🐻</span> to <span>🦏</span> to <span>🐯</span> to <span>🦥</span> and what not... 
            <br>Post anything you want to regarding 
            any particular species that is found in this habitat and let
            others know about it. You can post about a campaign or a fund raising organisation
            or even some random facts about your favorite species.
        </p>
    <% }%>
    <% if(community == 'ocean') { %>
        <h1 class="text-center header"><span>🌊</span> Seas and Oceans <span>🌊</span></h1>
        <p class="text-center description">There is a huge variety of wonderful species that you can 
            find in this habitat.<br> From <span>🐬</span> to <span>🐙</span> to <span>🦀</span> to <span>🐠</span> to <span>🐳</span> to <span>🐢</span> to <span>🦞</span> to <span>🦦</span> and what not... 
            <br>Post anything you want to regarding 
            any particular species that is found in this habitat and let
            others know about it. You can post about a campaign or a fund raising organisation
            or even some random facts about your favorite species.
        </p>
    <% }%>
    <% if(community == 'rainforest') { %>
        <h1 class="text-center header"><span>🌳</span> Tropical Rainforests <span>🌳</span></h1>
        <p class="text-center description">There is a huge variety of wonderful species that you can 
            find in this habitat.<br> From <span>🐸</span> to <span>🐊</span> to <span>🐍</span> to <span>🐦</span> to <span>🦜</span> to <span>🐨</span> to <span>🦋</span> to <span>🦚</span> and what not... 
            <br>Post anything you want to regarding 
            any particular species that is found in this habitat and let
            others know about it. You can post about a campaign or a fund raising organisation
            or even some random facts about your favorite species.
        </p>
    <% }%>
    <% if(community == 'desert') { %>
        <h1 class="text-center header"><span>🌵</span> Deserts <span>🌵</span></h1>
        <p class="text-center description">There is a huge variety of wonderful species that you can 
            find in this habitat.<br> From <span>🐪</span> to <span>🐍</span> to <span>🦂</span> to <span>🦊</span> to <span>🦎</span> to <span>🐫</span> and what not... 
            <br>Post anything you want to regarding 
            any particular species that is found in this habitat and let
            others know about it. You can post about a campaign or a fund raising organisation
            or even some random facts about your favorite species.
        </p>
    <% }%>
    <h2 class="text-center header">Submit a post!</h2>
    <div class="form">
        <form action= "/<%= community %>/feed " method="POST">
            <div class="form-floating mb-4">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="floatingInput" name="name">
                <label for="floatingInput">Author Name</label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-floating mb-3">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="floatingInput" name="title">
                <label for="floatingInput">Post Title</label>
            </div>
            <h1 class="mb-4 header">Post Type:</h1>
            <div class="form-check mb-3">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="charity" id="flexRadioDefault1">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="flexRadioDefault1">
                    NGOs/Charities
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check mb-3">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="support" id="flexRadioDefault2">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="flexRadioDefault2">
                    Support Groups
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check mb-3">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="trivia" id="flexRadioDefault3">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="flexRadioDefault3">
                    General Trivia
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-floating mb-3">
                <textarea class="form-control" id="floatingTextarea" style="width: 100%;height:400px;resize: none;" name="post"></textarea>
                <label for="floatingTextarea">Post Content</label>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary mb-3 form-control" style="width:20%">Submit!</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>